Title: Trattoria Trippa
Note: Traditional Lombardy dishes done with inventive twists. Be sure to order their beloved vitello tonnato, tripe or Milanese risotto with grilled bone marrow. It’s an unfussy place that knows exactly how to do food just right.

Title: Trattoria Mirta
Note: makes an excellent bowl of minestrone garnished with goat cheese, if you’re lucky enough to catch it on the ever-changing menu.
